<li id="cite_note-81"><b><a href="#cite_ref-81" title="">^</a></b> Walters, 192.</li>
<li id="cite_note-82"><b><a href="#cite_ref-82" title="">^</a></b> Walters, 10.</li>
<li id="cite_note-83"><b><a href="#cite_ref-83" title="">^</a></b> Foner, 256.</li>
